Package: xorp
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: eXtensible Open Router Platform
 XORP is the eXtensible Open Router Platform. It implements a number of
 network protocols such as BGP, OSPF, RIP/RIPng, IGMP/MLD and PIM-SM.

Package: xorp-doc
Architecture: all
Description: The documentation for XORP router platform
 XORP is the eXtensible Open Router Platform. It implements a number of
 network protocols such as BGP, OSPF, RIP/RIPng, IGMP/MLD and PIM-SM.
 This is the documentation for XORP in PDF format. It is also available
 from project's WEB site: http//www.xorp.org/
